		<Backstory>Orkoth is a famous smith from the Gnomish fortress Arak-Kazar. It was destroyed along with every other Gnome fortress during the Cataclysm. Since then, Orkoth has wandered the lands trying to find a purpose for his existence. Along with the rebirth of civilization taking place, he has rekindled his old interest of weapon- and armor-smithing. Orkoth is a master smith, one of the Forgelords of Arak-Kazar. His knowledge would be invaluable to anyone who has the foresight to recruit him.

He can be quite conventional and insists that people address him as "Orkoth, Forgelord". He is also known to throw a tantrum when those he supervises produce something that is less than perfect. Despite this, he is a supreme teacher and any who follow his rough but just guidance will soon stand out amongst the rest.
